## 📋 List

### Defining

```python
lis1 = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
```

### Accessing (Indexing)

```python
lis1[2]    # 3
lis1[-1]   # 5
lis1[1:5]  # [2,3,4,5]
```

### Printing

```python
print(lis1[2])   # 3
print(lis1[-1])  # 5
print(lis1[1:5]) # [2, 3, 4, 5]
```

---

## 🔸 Tuple

### Defining

```python
tup1 = (10, 20, 30, 40, 50)
```

### Accessing

```python
tup1[2]
tup1[-1]
tup1[1:5]
```

### Printing

```python
print(tup1[2])   # 30
print(tup1[-1])  # 50
