## 🔁 Loops

### For Loop

```python
for i in [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]:
    print(i)
```

### Range Examples

```python
range(5)        # [0,1,2,3,4]
range(1,5)      # [1,2,3,4]
range(1,6)      # [1,2,3,4,5]
range(1,10,2)   # [1,3,5,7,9]
```

> **Note:** Range stops at **n-1**

---

### While Loop

```python
while condition:
    statement
```

---

## 🧪 Example (Loops)

```python
#!/usr/bin/python3

print(list(range(5)))
print(list(range(1, 5)))
print(list(range(1, 20, 2)))

for i in range(5):
    print(i)

lis1 = [10, 20, 30, 40, "Hi", "hello"]

for i in lis1:
    print(i)
```

---

## 🧪 Example (While Loop)

```python
var1 = 1

while var1 <= 10:
    print(var1)
    var1 = var1 + 1
```

